<div class="article">
	<h1>百盛员工快乐一日游蓝田汤峪清风山寨</h1>
	<div>
		<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;清晨我站在门前，欣赏着对面的大山，脚下的湖水，觉得山比往日更绿水比往日更清，空中的寨旗迎合着我喜悦的心情跳动，湖对岸马路上已经有过往的行人，我哼着小曲下山迎接就要到来的客人。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;今天是我们首次迎接肯德基60名员工来清风山寨度假，他们基本都是90后的青年，组织纪律性较差，所以百盛要求我方派一名教练带队指挥，考虑到他们太年轻，又不太服从管理，这个团只好由我来带。其实我就爱带年轻人，跟他们在一起自己仿佛也年轻了许多。快乐欢笑那就更不用提。终于看到了他们的大巴，司机在我的指挥下停好了车。果然如同他们领导所言，这群年轻人下车就大喊大叫又推又闹，这些我见惯了，这也是他们来的目的寻找快乐放松自己。还没等领导发话，他们已嚷着让我带他们去乐翻天。原本我们谈好的是先爬山，再吃午饭，饭后休息一个小时再玩乐翻天娱乐项目，可这些年轻人等不急都要先玩，看着大家一致的要求，他们领导只好同意。为了大家玩的更开心更起劲，再他们领导的配合下，我将他们分成三队，并以&ldquo;肯德基&rdquo;&ldquo;亮剑&rdquo;&ldquo;金鹰&rdquo;分别为每队的队名，再让每队选出自己的队长。我宣布了比赛的名称和比赛规则，大家在我的指挥下激烈有序的开始了过关比赛，两个多小时大家玩的开心尽兴酣畅淋漓。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;吃中午饭时，大家争抢着吃，看着就香。饭后这群年轻人可蔫下了，一个个拍着鼓鼓的肚皮懒洋洋的躺在吊床上，板凳上，大扑克的，搓麻将的，看报纸的，赏风景的，千姿百态。我拿着喇叭喊着大家去爬上，听到的是一致的回答：NO.当太阳下山的时候，他们开心的谢别了清风山寨。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/a5706411bd2ad45c96de3b6f3b49dd0c.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 清风山寨梅花桩</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/b39e68e6aed2cb59bdee65ced6621a3c.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/84a00551b5a5f45abc2f02619486942f.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;清风山寨 习武园</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/dfd89afe8fb92757adc05a1dbe0e3f54.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 清风山寨之勇士桥</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/be750bcfe64a2a5bae439dc0aefe9ff6.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;清风山寨之走吊楼</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img width="500" height="333" alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/9fb2ec5b95405055bdddaa8e09c59171.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;肯德基员工在闯关</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/5ff353838ca1c45b9a40c785ce1daeb1.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 别看我小我走的很好</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/0b705ad39b4ce55188b10004bf047706.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;清风山寨之情侣桥</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/5a1ac1c2ad024a509ffcf13e0fbbde8d.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/163be3273fb5e75babfd1d16b972be9e.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 清风山寨之七星八杠无底断步桥</p><p style="text-align: center; "><img alt="" src="../uploads/Image/20110720/9aceafdaf3f08954a60820d1eccc57a7.jpg" /></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 肯德基在过云梯桥</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本位原创于www.qingfengshanzhai.com</p>
